lead_paragraph: Mercedes Russell had 15 points and 11 rebounds as No. 23 Tennessee defeated Arkansas 75-57 on Thursday to give Lady Volunteers coach Holly Warlick her 100th career victory.

headline.print_headline: Warlick Wins 100th as No. 23 Lady Vols Beat Arkansas 75-57
